title: BONUS - Losing Control? Here’s Why That’s A Good Thing.
description:
This isn't the first time the world's been left asking big questions. When our world crumbles, the things we've been chasing that aren't God are exposed and can leave us hopeless. But there is a great hope for us. Let's dive in!

Join us every week on IF:TV: ifgathering.com/tv
